textBox.richText: This is another cool one! The idea is that science is wrong, or something. This one also has that sort of “realistic” tone to it. The sprites were hard to get in though... The Robo-Eevee one was more customly made, but the Ghost-Eevee was pretty much completely stolen from somebody through Google Images... OH WELL. This one should send shivers down your spine... and if it doesn’t, well, too bad. ALSO THE IDEA FOR THE HACK WAS STOLEN FROM THE GIRL. Whatever that means. Also, please notice that the Robo-Eevee has no nature, and that the ghost Eevee has the same nature as the one that “died.”
